dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.systemtemplate.fibex.fibexcore.corecommunication.timing

Interface IEventControlledTiming

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity

    public interface IEventControlledTiming
extends IEntity
    IEventControlledTiming: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    Specification of a event driven sending behavior. The PDU is sent n (numberOfRepeat + 1) times separated by the repetitionPeriod. If numberOfRepeats = 0, then the Pdu is sent just once.

    GENERATED CODE. DO NOT CHANGE!
